"INCREASED REFLEXES"

Increased reflexes allows an adept to move faster in combat. Each level
adds +1D6 initiative dice and 2 reaction.

^WSee Also: ABILITIES^n

Also

Category: ^gHEALTH^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

Each Increased Reflexes spell increases initiative dice by the number of the
spell (+1, +2 or +3). Force determines the difficulty to dispell, as well as
drain. This spells will not work on anyone whose initiative is already 
modified.

^WSee Also: CAST^n
